{"title":"onion_by_organization_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"This panel shows the **evolution of the community structure split by organization** based on **onion analysis**.

* **Core**: those contributing **80% of the activity**.
* **Regular**: those contributing the next **15% of the activity**.
* **Casual**: those contributing  the **last 5% of the activity**
